# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:16
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_1bfa8620:

    # "As we work on our assignments in English class, Mrs. McGee comes by my desk and puts her hand on my shoulder."
    "Mientras trabajamos en nuestros deberes en la clase de inglés, la Sra. McGee se acerca a mi pupitre y me pone la mano en el hombro."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:17
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_e0a44997:

    # et "[pcname], could you stay a bit after class. I need to talk to you about your Canterbury Tales essay."
    et "[pcname], ¿podrías quedarte un rato después de clase? Necesito hablar contigo sobre tu ensayo de Los cuentos de Canterbury."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:18
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_1ca80c77:

    # pc "Yes, ma'am."
    pc "Sí, señora."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:21
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_336feedb:

    # "Through the rest of the class, I worry about what she could want to talk to me about. It has been a week since we finished Canterbury tales, and I thought I did pretty good on that essay."
    "Durante el resto de la clase, me preocupo por lo que querrá decirme. Ha pasado una semana desde que terminamos Los cuentos de Canterbury, y creo que me salió bastante bien ese ensayo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:22
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_e846710c:

    # "Finally, class ends and all the other students start out the door, but I stay behind."
    "Por fin, termina la clase y todos los demás alumnos salen por la puerta, pero yo me quedo atrás."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:25
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_91684385:

    # et "Thanks for staying a little late. I just had a couple of questions I wanted to ask you about your essay."
    et "Gracias por quedarte un rato más. Solo tenía un par de preguntas que quería hacerte sobre tu ensayo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:26
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_63023601:

    # pc "Okay."
    pc "De acuerdo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:27
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_64a3bccf:

    # et "The assignment was to choose your favorite story from The Canterbury Tales and write a synopsis and an analysis of the story as it relates to modern storytelling."
    et "La tarea consistía en elegir tu historia favorita de Los cuentos de Canterbury y escribir una sinopsis y un análisis de la historia en relación con la narrativa moderna."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:28
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_bf5ca486:

    # et "You chose The Miller's Tale. Why is that particular tale your favorite?"
    et "Elegiste El cuento del molinero. ¿Por qué es ese cuento en concreto tu favorito?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:33
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_90b318a5:

    # et "Yes, I suppose it is."
    et "Sí, supongo que lo es."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:34
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_5b41f62c:

    # et "It is funny to read about this Miller whose beautiful wife is having sex with men behind his back, and he's completely oblivious."
    et "Es divertido leer sobre este molinero cuya hermosa esposa se acuesta con otros hombres a sus espaldas, y él no se da cuenta de nada."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:35
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_23f8de94:

    # pc "I was more talking about the fart jokes, but yeah that's pretty funny too."
    pc "Me refería más bien a los chistes sobre pedos, pero sí, eso también es bastante divertido."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:39
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_589e3574:

    # et "Yes it is."
    et "Sí, lo es."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:40
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_a1b1b58c:

    # et "I think it's interesting to hear that is the reason why it's your favorite."
    et "Me parece interesante que esa sea la razón por la que es tu favorito."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:42
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_225d6c9f:

    # et "I was wondering if it might be your favorite because it's about a man whose beautiful wife is having sex with men behind his back?"
    et "Me preguntaba si quizá fuera tu favorito porque trata de un hombre cuya hermosa esposa se acuesta con otros hombres a sus espaldas."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:43
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_5ff3823e:

    # pc "I don't know. Maybe?"
    pc "No lo sé. ¿Quizá?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:46
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_47e5b0f5:

    # et "Do you like the idea of having sex with a married woman?"
    et "¿Te gusta la idea de acostarte con una mujer casada?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:47
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_c4594e48:

    # et "About humiliating her impotent husband? Showing him how a woman should be treated?"
    et "¿De humillar a su marido impotente? ¿De enseñarle cómo se debe tratar a una mujer?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:50
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_9a72f950:

    # et "I thought you might."
    et "Me imaginaba que te gustaría."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:54
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_26f420dd:

    # et "Oh, I'm sorry then. I misread something."
    et "Oh, entonces lo siento. He malinterpretado algo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:55
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_bec3fa51:

    # et "The essay is very good. You're doing great in class, [pcname]. I'll stop bothering you about anything… outside of class."
    et "El ensayo está muy bien. Lo estás haciendo muy bien en clase, [pcname]. Dejaré de molestarte con cualquier cosa… fuera de clase."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:56
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_d07e9fd4:

    # pc "Okay, Mrs. McGee. I'll talk to you later."
    pc "Vale, Sra. McGee. Hablamos luego."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:57
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_dc1e70f2:

    # et "Bye, [pcname]."
    et "Adiós, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:59
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_491dbae2:

    # "The rest of my classes pass without incident, then it's time to go to work."
    "El resto de mis clases transcurren sin incidentes, y luego llega la hora de ir a trabajar."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:63
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_cc5b1913:

    # et "There is a lot of language in the story that is difficult to understand. It's not exactly Old English, it's more like Old English slang."
    et "Hay mucho lenguaje en la historia que es difícil de entender. No es exactamente inglés antiguo, es más bien jerga del inglés antiguo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:64
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_08d83e37:

    # et "Such as the line where Chaucer says that Nicholas grabs Alisoun \"by the queynte.\" Do you understand what that means?"
    et "Como la frase en la que Chaucer dice que Nicholas agarra a Alisoun «por la queynte». ¿Entiendes lo que significa eso?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:69
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_3a9f8ae2:

    # "I lean in and kiss her lips. I half-expect her to pull away from me, but she doesn't. She returns my kiss passionately, her tongue slipping in between my lips."
    "Me inclino y beso sus labios. Casi espero que se aparte de mí, pero no lo hace. Me devuelve el beso apasionadamente, deslizando su lengua entre mis labios."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:70
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_88e770e5:

    # "She presses herself against me, obviously hungry for more."
    "Se aprieta contra mí, claramente hambrienta de más."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:82
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_b851c10c:

    # "I step up to her, reaching down between her legs and grabbing her while pressing my lips against hers."
    "Me acerco a ella, meto la mano entre sus piernas y la agarro mientras presiono mis labios contra los suyos."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:83
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_6836d91b:

    # "I half-expect her to pull away from me, or to yell out, but after the initial surprise of my touch, she starts pressing herself against me, kissing me back with a hunger, grinding her hips against my hand."
    "Casi espero que se aparte de mí, o que grite, pero tras la sorpresa inicial de mi tacto, empieza a apretarse contra mí, devolviéndome el beso con avidez, frotando sus caderas contra mi mano."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:84
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_a8ed1eb1:

    # "I could feel how warm and wet she was even through her dress."
    "Podía sentir lo caliente y húmeda que estaba incluso a través de su vestido."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:86
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_75e7549b:

    # et "That's too bad."
    et "Qué pena."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:89
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_ebc0b6c6:

    # et "Okay, [pcname], that's all I wanted to ask you. Your essay is very good and you're doing great in class."
    et "Vale, [pcname], eso es todo lo que quería preguntarte. Tu redacción es muy buena y lo estás haciendo muy bien en clase."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:90
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_367c3a3f:

    # et "You better get to your next class now."
    et "Será mejor que vayas ya a tu siguiente clase."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:91
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_1ca80c77_1:

    # pc "Yes, ma'am."
    pc "Sí, señora."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:92
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_56ef2b64:

    # "I leave her class and walk to the next, not exactly sure what all of that was about."
    "Salgo de su clase y camino hacia la siguiente, sin saber muy bien de qué iba todo eso."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:93
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_f32bd31b:

    # "The rest of my classes pass without incident, then it is time to go to work."
    "El resto de mis clases transcurren sin incidentes, y luego llega la hora de ir al trabajo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:99
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_eb447035:

    # "Then, just as quickly and passionately as her kiss started, it ends when she forcefully pushes me away."
    "Entonces, tan rápido y apasionadamente como comenzó su beso, este termina cuando ella me empuja con fuerza."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:100
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_815cee6e:

    # et "No, [pcname]. We can't do this. I'm married and I love my husband."
    et "No, [pcname]. No podemos hacer esto. Estoy casada y amo a mi marido."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:101
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_bbb49d81:

    # pc "But…"
    pc "Pero…"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:102
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_baa067de:

    # et "No buts. You should go."
    et "Sin peros. Deberías irte."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:103
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_6d9994c4:

    # pc "I don't understand."
    pc "No lo entiendo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:104
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_4f85d033:

    # et "This is not the time or place for this sort of outburst. We won't be discussing this anymore right now."
    et "Este no es el momento ni el lugar para este tipo de arrebatos. No vamos a seguir hablando de esto ahora mismo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:105
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_1f1c51ca:

    # et "Your essay is very good and you're doing great in class. Now get to your next class, we're done here."
    et "Tu redacción es muy buena y lo estás haciendo muy bien en clase. Ahora ve a tu siguiente clase, aquí hemos terminado."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:106
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_f72d2804:

    # pc "Uh… okay. Bye, Mrs. McGee."
    pc "Eh… vale. Adiós, Sra. McGee."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:109
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_0ccd1147:

    # "I leave her classroom, not exactly sure what had just happened."
    "Salgo de su aula, sin saber muy bien qué acaba de pasar."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:110
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_213f5c51:

    # "She's playing some sort of game and it feels like I'm just along for the ride."
    "Ella está jugando a algún tipo de juego y siento que yo solo estoy ahí para acompañarla."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:111
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_78fe728d:

    # "I guess I'll have to wait and see what happens next."
    "Supongo que tendré que esperar a ver qué pasa después."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:114
translate spanish mrsmcgee7_0d69ab43:

    # "I go to my next class and the rest of the day passes without incident, then it's time to go to work."
    "Voy a mi siguiente clase y el resto del día transcurre sin incidentes, luego llega la hora de ir al trabajo."

